title: Halloween Tripeaks v1.0.15
description:
Bring back the happy haunted home of Frankenstein and his Witch bride in this spooky solitaire treat! 

This is the spooky version of the popular card game called Tripeaks.

FEATURES

- Super addictive solitaire fun.
- Great graphics themed for Halloween.
- Intuitive controls.

Enjoy Halloween Tripeaks the most fun, spooky solitaire game around.
